document.full_text: on the eve of mr. hussein's birthday, a new youtube video landed that depicts an actual phone call between a member of iraq's parliament and a man who claimed to be mr. hussein.
document.title: baghdad journal: hold the phone! that sure sounds like saddam hussein.
